										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Puedes leer perfectamente el artículo aquí, pero si quieres disfrutar al 100% de la experiencia al completo, lo mejor es leerlo en MacSfera: <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.MacSfera.com/imagenes-del-interior-del-campus-de-apple/">Imágenes del interior del campus de Apple</a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-de-Apple.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-de-Apple.jpg" alt="Campus de Apple" title="Campus de Apple" width="550" height="366" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6649" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-de-Apple.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-de-Apple-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>Es raro ver imágenes de puertas a dentro de <strong><a href="https://www.macsfera.com/" title="Apple" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple</a></strong>, muy raro de hecho, pero han hecho una recopilación bastante amplia en la que <strong>muestran el interior del actual campus de la empresa, el <a href="https://www.macsfera.com/taginfinite-loop" title="Infinite Loop" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Infinite Loop</a>.</strong></p>
<p><span id="more-6648"></span></p>
<p>Recordemos que <strong>Apple está planificando hacer un nuevo campus</strong>, bastante novedoso la verdad que pretende ahorrar energía y congregar más trabajadores.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Mesa-de-recepción-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Mesa-de-recepción-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg" alt="Mesa de recepción Infinite Loop Apple" title="Mesa de recepción Infinite Loop Apple" width="550" height="355" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6650" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Mesa-de-recepción-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Mesa-de-recepción-Infinite-Loop-Apple-300x194.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="" title="Campus Apple Infinite Loop" width="369" height="492" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6651" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 369w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 369px) 100vw, 369px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasarela-de-edificio-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasarela-de-edificio-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg" alt="" title="Pasarela de edificio Infinite Loop Apple" width="550" height="167" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6652" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasarela-de-edificio-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasarela-de-edificio-Infinite-Loop-Apple-300x91.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sillón-descanso-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sillón-descanso-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Sillón descanso Apple Infinite Loop" title="Sillón descanso Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="413" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6653" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sillón-descanso-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sillón-descanso-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Anuncio-iPad-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Anuncio-iPad-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg" alt="Anuncio iPad Infinite Loop Apple" title="Anuncio iPad Infinite Loop Apple" width="550" height="828" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6654" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Anuncio-iPad-Infinite-Loop-Apple.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Anuncio-iPad-Infinite-Loop-Apple-199x300.jpg 199w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>Después de ver un poco del interior del campus pasamos a la <strong><a href="https://www.macsfera.com/tagapple-store" title="Apple Store" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Apple Store</a></strong> de la compañía, el «único lugar» donde se pueden hacer fotos y <strong>la única tienda oficial que vende diferentes objetos no tecnológicos con el logotipo de la manzana mordida,</strong> si nos fijamos no se parece en nada a las <strong>Apple Store</strong> comunes.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Apple Store Infinite Loop" title="Apple Store Infinite Loop" width="550" height="368" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6655" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop-300x201.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-de-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-de-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Apple Store de Infinite Loop" title="Apple Store de Infinite Loop" width="550" height="368" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6656" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-de-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Apple-Store-de-Infinite-Loop-300x201.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Merchandise-de-Apple-Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Merchandise-de-Apple-Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Merchandise de Apple Apple Store Infinite Loop" title="Merchandise de Apple Apple Store Infinite Loop" width="550" height="368" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6657" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Merchandise-de-Apple-Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Merchandise-de-Apple-Apple-Store-Infinite-Loop-300x201.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>A lo largo de mi vida he visitado muchos lavabos de diferentes restaurantes o locales, cada uno de los carteles que he visto eran muy curiosos, <strong>no podía ser menos en este campus que muestra un dibujo pixelado de una mujer y un hombre para diferenciarlos.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Mujer-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Mujer-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg.jpg" alt="Cartel de Mujer Servicios Apple Infinite Loop.jpg" title="Cartel de Mujer Servicios Apple Infinite Loop.jpg" width="550" height="365" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6658" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Mujer-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Mujer-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg-300x199.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Hombre-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Hombre-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Cartel de Hombre Servicios Apple Infinite Loop" title="Cartel de Hombre Servicios Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="365" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6659" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Hombre-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cartel-de-Hombre-Servicios-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x199.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasillo-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasillo-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Pasillo campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Pasillo campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="410" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6660" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasillo-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pasillo-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x224.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Oficina-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Oficina-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Oficina Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Oficina Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="412" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6661" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Oficina-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Oficina-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Hall-del-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Hall-del-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Hall del campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Hall del campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="412" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6662" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Hall-del-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Hall-del-campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>Aquí os presentamos <strong>la cafetería,</strong> un lugar donde poder comer tranquilamente aunque como defecto tiene que <strong>Apple</strong> no pone la comida gratis, <strong>ni si quiera para sus empleados,</strong> pero eso si, es barata y saludable.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-Capus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-Capus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Cafetería Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Cafetería Capus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="412" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6663" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-Capus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-Capus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Cafetería del Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Cafetería del Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="733" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6664" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Cafetería-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>Cuando los empleados necesitan un descanso pueden ir a la «<strong>Rec room</strong>» a jugar a algunos juegos o ir al exterior para jugar al baloncesto, al voleibol o hacer deporte en el gimnasio.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Rec room Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Rec room Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="412" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6665" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Rec room del Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Rec room del Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="365" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6666" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Rec-room-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x199.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pista-de-baloncesto-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pista-de-baloncesto-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt=" Pista de baloncesto Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title=" Pista de baloncesto Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="480" height="640" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6667" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pista-de-baloncesto-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 480w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Pista-de-baloncesto-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-225x300.jpg 225w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Gimnasio-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Gimnasio-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Gimnasio Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Gimnasio Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="360" height="278" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6668" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Gimnasio-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 360w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Gimnasio-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x232.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" /></a></p>
<p>Como cualquier empresa, <strong>dispone de salas de reuniones en las que hablar a la plantilla, hablar entre ellos o dar pequeñas conferencias presentando nuevos productos.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-conferencia-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-conferencia-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Sala de conferencia Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Sala de conferencia Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="413" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6669" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-conferencia-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-conferencia-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-reuniones-Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-reuniones-Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Sala de reuniones Campus Apple Infinite Loop" title="Sala de reuniones Campus Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="439" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6670" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-reuniones-Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-reuniones-Campus-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x239.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-Keynote-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-Keynote-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Sala de Keynote Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Sala de Keynote Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="359" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6671" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-Keynote-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Sala-de-Keynote-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x196.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>Cuando salió a la luz el antenagate del iPhone 4, <strong>Apple</strong> publicó una serie de fotos en las que mostraba los <strong>laboratorios que tenian para medir todos los parámetros de las ondas de comunicación de su teléfono.</strong></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-de-Apple.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-de-Apple.jpg" alt="Laboratorio de telefonía de Apple" title="Laboratorio de telefonía de Apple" width="550" height="343" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6672" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-de-Apple.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-de-Apple-300x187.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Laboratorio de telefonía del Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Laboratorio de telefonía del Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="343" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6673" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-del-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x187.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-Apple-Campus-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-Apple-Campus-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Laboratorio de telefonía Apple Campus Infinite Loop" title="Laboratorio de telefonía Apple Campus Infinite Loop" width="550" height="343" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6674" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-Apple-Campus-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Laboratorio-de-telefonía-Apple-Campus-Infinite-Loop-300x187.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
<p>Por último y para acabar, <strong>el lugar probablemente más secreto de todo el campus,</strong> aquel que hace que los rumores se disparen y donde empieza cualquier producto: <strong>El departamento de diseño.</strong> En la foto vemos a <strong><a href="https://www.macsfera.com/tagjonathan-ive" title="Jonathan Ive" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Jonathan Ive</a> </strong>con un <strong><a href="https://www.macsfera.com/tagmacbook-air" title="MacBook Air" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MacBook Air</a></strong>.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Departamento-de-diseño-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg"><img style=' display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;'  src="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Departamento-de-diseño-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg" alt="Departamento de diseño Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" title="Departamento de diseño Campus de Apple Infinite Loop" width="550" height="309" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6675" srcset="https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Departamento-de-diseño-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop.jpg 550w, https://www.MacSfera.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/Departamento-de-diseño-Campus-de-Apple-Infinite-Loop-300x169.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px" /></a></p>
